    "title": "曇りの日の1ページ",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ある日、1人廊下を歩いていると、物憂げな\r\n顔をしたライスシャワーが目に入った。",
            "enText": "One day, as I was walking alone \nin the corridor, I saw a languid-looking \nrice shower.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 120,
            "pathId": 7494475990889514126,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ライスシャワー",
            "enName": "Rice Shower",
            "jpText": "うぅ。\r\nどうしよう……どうしよう……。",
            "enText": "Ugh. What should I do?… What should I do?…",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "何かあったの？",
                    "enText": "What's going on?",
                    "nextBlock": 3
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 113,
                    "pathId": 6010595535928667687
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": 5576054668046861842
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6715944715085339990,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ライスシャワー",
            "enName": "Rice Shower",
            "jpText": "ひゃあっ！？\r\n……あ、こ、こんにちは……！",
            "enText": "Hyah!… Oh, hello there…!",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 55,
                    "pathId": -8352295057115677412
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": 5160542484373397007
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2190796945596008073,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ライスシャワー",
            "enName": "Rice Shower",
            "jpText": "あのね……天気予報で、\r\n『明日は豪雨ですよ』って言ってたの。",
            "enText": "You know, the… weather forecast said that \nthere would be torrential rain tomorrow.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": 2404712797656197298
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": 2780096762845012487
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6158632043567562796,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ライスシャワー",
            "enName": "Rice Shower",
            "jpText": "けどライス……レースが近いから\r\n明日はいっぱい走りたいなって思って……。",
            "enText": "But Rice… race is coming up, so I thought \nI'd run a lot tomorrow…",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "体育館を借りて走ろう！",
                    "enText": "Let's hire a gym and run!",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "てるてる坊主を作ろう！",
                    "enText": "Let's make a teru teru bozu!",
                    "nextBlock": 12
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": -1564557431305076761
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": -8917687070738093739
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7592752332302297355,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "コースは再現できないものの、\r\n体育館を借りて直線距離で加速する\nトレーニングができると提案した。",
            "enText": "Although the course could not be recreated, \nit was suggested that the gymnasium could be \nhired to train the athletes to accelerate in \na straight line.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 108,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 133,
                    "pathId": -1419305015551711858
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 180,
                    "pathId": 4417855467753378152
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": 5674376386070591663
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4459146688949756228,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ライスシャワー",
            "enName": "Rice Shower",
            "jpText": "それ、いいかも。\r\n……あっ！",
            "enText": "That could be good… Ah!",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -7416875680197968510
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 8916349078907779733
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": -6195807898516547229
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1178485131010709370,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ライスシャワー",
            "enName": "Rice Shower",
            "jpText": "けど、それだと他の子が体育館を\r\n使えなくなっちゃうんじゃないかな……？",
            "enText": "But wouldn't that mean that other kids \nwouldn't be able to use the gym…?",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 6583253707626500598
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": 4982637152904648297
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6074683185980246280,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "他のウマ娘も誘うので、彼女たちと一緒に\r\nトレーニングすればいいと言うと、\nライスシャワーは安心したようだった。",
            "enText": "Rice Shower seemed relieved when we \ntold her that we would invite the other \ngirls to train with us, and that she \ncould do so with them.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 118,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 158,
                    "pathId": -6696501919016809350
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": -3864945933949547962
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3961555249543784365,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ライスシャワー",
            "enName": "Rice Shower",
            "jpText": "……ありがとう！\r\nえへへ、楽しみだなぁ！",
            "enText": "Thanks…! Ehehe, I'm looking forward to it!",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 65,
                    "pathId": -3375900419673374416
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": -1715350984460404046
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7240895312631936322,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "かくして開催されたトレーニングは、\r\n大きなトラブルもなく、無事に終了した。",
            "enText": "The training session went \noff without a hitch.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 17,
                    "pathId": -9050672192752146376
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 17,
                    "pathId": -6489357484888940128
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7509806957145769230,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ライスシャワー",
            "enName": "Rice Shower",
            "jpText": "うん……！\r\nたくさん作ったら、きっと晴れるよねっ。",
            "enText": "Yeah…! If you make lots of them, \nit will be sunny, I'm sure.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 87,
                    "pathId": 6655224570821415571
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": 7775221422489526430
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8074513418007264806,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ライスシャワー",
            "enName": "Rice Shower",
            "jpText": "かわいい子……作ろうね。\r\nライスは青いてるてる坊主がいいなぁ……。",
            "enText": "Let's make a cute little… I like the blue \nteru teru bozu for rice…",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 112,
                    "pathId": 823006864713301261
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": -3968977987857939192
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4224976503332378918,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ライスシャワー",
            "enName": "Rice Shower",
            "jpText": "……あっ！\r\nでもでもっ、やっぱりだめだよ……。",
            "enText": "… Ah! But still, you can't…",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 76,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -6520102432695333050
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": 8344003151495727883
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8062299429379980059,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ライスシャワー",
            "enName": "Rice Shower",
            "jpText": "ライスがやると、もっと大雨になっちゃう\r\nかも。だから……。",
            "enText": "If Rice does it, it will probably rain even \nharder. So please visit…",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "俺もいっぱい作るから、大丈夫",
                    "enText": "I'll make lots of food too, don't worry.",
                    "nextBlock": 16
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "私もいっぱい作るから、大丈夫",
                    "enText": "Don't worry, I make a lot too!",
                    "nextBlock": 16
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": 2303279778644467879
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": -6115232682607183681
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8281835711190992053,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ライスシャワー",
            "enName": "Rice Shower",
            "jpText": "……そっか。それなら安心だね！\r\nライス、がんばるよっ……！",
            "enText": "… I see. That's a relief! \nI'll do my best, Rice…!",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": 5013424398135305976
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": 4882108030535214881
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8635330486866603177,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ライスシャワーの願いが通じたのか、\r\n次の日は見事な快晴になった。",
            "enText": "The next day was a beautiful sunny day, as \nif Rice Shower had been answered.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
